<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="celebrate-v">celebrate <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'selɪbreɪt/    美 /'selɪbreɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>庆祝：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To celebrate the end of our exams, my friends and I went to a fast food restaurant.
为庆祝考试结束，我和朋友们去了一家快餐店。</p><footer>2013 陕西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Jack’s passed his exam. We are going out to celebrate.
杰克通过了考试，我们要出去庆祝一下。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>赞扬；歌颂：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His work celebrates the energy and enthusiasm of the young.
他的作品歌颂了年轻人的朝气和热情。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>celebrated /'selɪbreɪtɪd/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>They’re going to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (庆祝) their victory with music and dancing.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. celebrate  </p></div>